# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
*          text=auto

#### C# files ####
*.cs       text eol=lf diff=csharp
*.cshtml   text eol=lf diff=html
*.csx      text eol=lf diff=csharp
*.sln      text eol=crlf
*.csproj   text eol=crlf

#### Sqlite files ####
*.sqlite   binary

